.TH "LIGHTNING-PAY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-pay \- pay a BOLT-11 invoice
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning pay
[\fIsubcommand\fR] [\fIargs\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.nf
lightning pay — pay a BOLT-11 invoice.

Implements: BOLT-11 payment per FEAT-173.
  share/doc/lightning/standards/bolts/11-payment-encoding.md

Usage:
  lightning pay <bolt11>
                [--max-fee-sat N]    # cap routing fee
                [--timeout S]        # give up after S seconds
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR lightning (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Part of the \fBlightning\fR educational Lightning Network frontend.
